hong kong bank rais prime one-half point to 6.5 pct hongkong and shanghai bank corp and standard charter bank rais their prime rate one-half point to 6.5 pct , effect tuesday , the associ of bank said . the associ said in a statement deposit rate have also been increas by 1/4 to 1/2 percentag point . the bank last announc an adjust on februari 28 when they rais the prime rate by one point to six pct . the deposit interest rate are now save and 24 hour two pct , seven-day call , one week and two week 2-1/4 pct , one month and two month 2-3/4 pct , three and six month 3-1/4 pct , nine month 3-1/2 pct and 12 month four pct .